ygData.msgSnippet: The new skills are 51+ and if you did not know are gained through an alternate experience bar.  In other words, gives people at level 60 a reason to exp grind
ygData.messageBody:
The new skills are 51+ and if you did not know are gained through an
alternate experience bar. In other words, gives people at level 60 a
reason to exp grind again.
